Package: XentonalAssistant
Type: Package
Title: A Composer's Assistant for Xentonal Music
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "M. Edward (Ed)", "Borasky",
      email = "znmeb@algocompsynth.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: XentonalAssistant is an interactive tool for
    composers of xentonal music. It provides tools for
    creating recorded music using scales other than the
    standard twelve tone equal tempered scale.
